{"tid":2282571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗泰肯定國旗單野被人捉住痛腳","createTime":"2020-11-12T02:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T09:55:13.000Z","uid":237459,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12f97d37cef6e6fc22e364738affb25b6678d401","tid":2282571,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"湯鳩華叫十一哥<br />\n你叫國旗哥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港澳辦讚揚鄭松泰留守「值得肯定」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2282505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2282505</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀<br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉新界西參選人、熱血公民鄭松泰，向選舉主任回信，重申絕不支持「香港獨立」的主張，並對倒插國旗一事表達歉意。<br />\n<br />\n選舉主任昨日去信鄭松泰，就2016年一次立法會會議上，他將部分國區與區旗展示品倒轉放，被裁定侮辱國旗及區旗罪成，詢問他是否同意有關言行顯示他無意真正及忠誠地擁護《基本法》，及效忠特區的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰回信說，在法庭判決後，經過觀察和反省，認為當年所做的事，表達方式確實不對，及後再無做對國旗和區旗不敬的事。由於沒有官方或公眾再次提問當年的事，他無法表達對國家和《基本法》的敬意，難得選舉主任來函詢問，特此表達歉意。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540353-20200728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540353-20200728.htm&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=fdf34c9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540353-20200728.htm&h=05cd368a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540353-20200728.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d4baa76120b805319e267bdc7b655fb64e1589a9","tid":2282571,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce93cb58c69db603e5024f98fe033c0cc65a50d","tid":2282571,"uid":69650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"個死傻仔"},{"pid":"9b7ac9329af2c28896602059c5d67dfc